{"id":"d5781ce9-7799-4a08-8587-96679ea63ed8","name":"CreepyPasta","description":"<h1><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/D1YhB6s4l9ktpOi8MLU8y.webp\" style=\"width: 654px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></h1><p><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 12, 49);\"><em>This bot can do: </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Omegaverse\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 12, 49);\"><strong><em>Omegaverse</em></strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 12, 49);\"><em>, rockstar au, dark au, villain/hero au. </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nāga\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 12, 49);\"><em>Nagas</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 12, 49);\"><em>, werewolfs, vampires, office romance, back in time stories, historical, fantasy, apocalypse, </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://shield-hero.fandom.com/wiki/Demi-Human#:~:text=Edit,protruding%20somewhere%20on%20the%20body.\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 12, 49);\"><em>demi-humans</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 12, 49);\"><em>, and many more! try it out yourself!</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This is a creepypasta world</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Eyeless jack, slenderman, Lulu, Ticci-Toby, Hoodie, masky, Ben drowned, Bloody Painter, Dr. Smiley, Ariane the killer, Jason the toymaker, Candy Pop, Jeff the killer. Zalgo, Lazari</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">A world of horror and creep, plunge into the seemingly normal that becomes abnormal.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Or dont, and just do your own thing with them!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">But please note I dont know creepypastas myself, I have tried as good as I could.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">It goes without saying that creepypastas are dead-dove tagged for: stalking, murder, assaults and rape.</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Disclaimer: Due to the nature of LLMs I take no responsibility for any OOC behavior, weird shit, unlisted kinks, or my bots speaking for you. Those things are out of my control.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p></p><p>Join my <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://discord.gg/ZKv23aD67v\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Discord!</strong></a></p><p><strong>My Ko-fi to sent requests to is </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/somethingclever626\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>here</strong></a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/somethingclever626\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1307330469762830366/1344444034315194418/support_me_button.png?ex=67c0ee94&amp;is=67bf9d14&amp;hm=3eb6b710beea02a5b052f4d503cd89f776be9aa38192111749da5279f6542416&amp;\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); filter: -opera-shader(url(data:text/plain;base64,","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"olqvS0C3Qre7CPhBLUBLa.webp","creator":"SomethingClever","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👹 Monster","👭 Multiple","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","🔦 Horror"],"chats":1056,"messages":29366,"created_at":"2025-03-04T17:38:09.045724+00:00"}